        <div class="bb-intro-module__card-description">
                    <p>Texas lawmakers <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/texas-abortion-ban-exceptions-deaths">pushed for new exceptions to the state’s strict abortion ban</a> after we reported on the deaths of pregnant women whose miscarriages went untreated.</p>

