    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/segregation-academies">Segregation Academies</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/segregation-academies-demographic-data-private-schools">
                                    How Segregated Are Your Local Private Schools? We Made a Tool to Help You Find Out.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Our reporters mined a trove of data that revealed detailed demographic information about private schools. That helped us find illuminating stories about how those schools divide communities.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-berry-hawes">Jennifer Berry Hawes</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-01-18EST06:00">Jan. 18, 2025, 6 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
