    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/segregation-academies">Segregation Academies</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/propublica-private-school-demographics-lookup">
                                    ProPublica Releases New Private School Demographics Lookup
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Now you can look up detailed demographic information about thousands of private schools across the country and compare them to nearby public schools.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/sergio-hernandez">Sergio Hernández</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/nat-lash">Nat Lash</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/ken-schwencke">Ken Schwencke</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-01-16EST12:45">Jan. 16, 2025, 12:45 p.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    
                <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://projects.propublica.org/private-school-demographics">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/externals/_threeTwo400w/private-school-demographics-og-image-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg"
                    width="400"
                    height="267"
                    srcset="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/externals/_threeTwo400w/private-school-demographics-og-image-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg 400w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/externals/_threeTwo800w/private-school-demographics-og-image-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg 800w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/externals/_threeTwo1200w/private-school-demographics-og-image-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg 1200w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/externals/_threeTwo1600w/private-school-demographics-og-image-3x2_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg 1600w "
                    loading="lazy"
                    js-autosizes
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
